Red and Black

기초통계값 비교

최소값, 제1사분위수, 중위수, 산술평균, 제3사분위수, 최대값. 닮았나요?

comments_w$group <- class_roll0404$group[match(comments_w$id, class_roll0404$id)]
tapply(comments_w$total, comments_w$group, summary) %>% 
  pander

  • Red:

    Min. 1st Qu. Median Mean 3rd Qu. Max.
    0 5 7 6.061 7.9 10

  • Black:

    Min. 1st Qu. Median Mean 3rd Qu. Max.
    0 4.9 7 6.065 8 10

표준편차

tapply(comments_w$total, comments_w$group, sd) %>%
  pander
Red Black
2.663 2.74

댓글을 아직 한번도 올리지 않은 사람의 수효

tapply(comments_w$total == 0, comments_w$group, sum) %>%
  pander
Red Black
32 41

t-test

p-value 를 보고 판단하세요.

t.test(comments_w$total ~ comments_w$group) %>%
  pander

-0.02356 1009 0.9812 two.sided 6.061 6.065
